summary: From 10/22/18 - 10/25/18, the TwitchPresents marathon is LIVE this week with Pokémon: Battle Frontier! Episodes from season 9...
body:
From 10/22/18 - 10/25/18, the TwitchPresents marathon is LIVE this week with Pokémon: Battle Frontier!

Episodes from season 9 (the beginning of Pokémon USA, now TCPi, dubbing of the Pokémon anime) include the Mime Jr. joining Team Rocket, the 6 remaining Battle Frontier brains Ash has yet to face, May’s road to the Kanto Grand Festival, an Eevee egg, a newly evolved Donphan, a crying Bonsly, Grovyle in love, a cheeky Aipom, an introduction to Pokémon Rangers, Brock entering his first contest, a Team Rocket split, revisiting the Pewter gym, May & Max going back home to Hoenn, Gary’s surprise return, and much more!

There will be 11 episodes on Monday that will rerun 4 times just so you won’t miss the stream depending on your schedule: 10am | 2:50pm | 7:30pm | 12:10am | (PDT, UTC−07:00). While there will be 12 episodes are shown per day from Tuesday-Thursday that will rerun 4 times as well: 10am | 3:15pm | 8:20pm | 1:25am (PDT, UTC−07:00).

Watching with Twitch chat could be the best (or worst) experience you’ll ever have! But if you want a more comfy chat experience, feel free to talk/chat about the marathon in my Pokémon Discord server PokéTōku —> Invite link here :)
